{
  "stem": "323.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't think my relatives did what they could have done to get us out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I don't only blame the Germans, I blame the whole world now.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because, I mean, they, they could have done something, to raise money and get an affidavit to get people out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's the only way to get out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a quota system.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had a quota that would have been OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But you did need an affidavit, and you needed money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they used-- and now, I had about eight sets of relatives that had gotten out of Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And all the eight together couldn't raise enough money to get one family out?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't buy that anymore.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, everybody is dead, so there's nothing-- I mean, I can't blame anyone anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I just feel that they should have done more than they did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What happened when you were there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What happened next?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then, then things began to happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had to wear the Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- well, first in '38, we were kicked out of school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there were only the three of us-- my cousin, my sister, and I was standing outside crying.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, because we don't know what was happening.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we decided to walk home together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then my parents-- since most of the Jewish teachers were also dismissed, they did set up some schools for us, with Jewish teachers.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did attend these schools and some Hebrew school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the temple was still there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then we had to wear the Jewish star.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we weren't allowed to go swimming, I weren't allowed-- wasn't allowed to do anything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I wasn't allowed to go anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My mother was afraid to let us go out.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
